11#include "modules/audio_processing/agc2/saturation_protector_buffer.h"
12
13#include "rtc_base/checks.h"
14#include "rtc_base/numerics/safe_compare.h"
15
16namespace webrtc {
17
18SaturationProtectorBuffer::SaturationProtectorBuffer() = default;
19
20SaturationProtectorBuffer::~SaturationProtectorBuffer() = default;
21
22bool SaturationProtectorBuffer::operator==(
23 const SaturationProtectorBuffer& b) const {
24 RTC_DCHECK_LE(size_, buffer_.size());
25 RTC_DCHECK_LE(b.size_, b.buffer_.size());
26 if (size_ != b.size_) {
27 return false;
28 }
29 for (int i = 0, i0 = FrontIndex(), i1 = b.FrontIndex(); i < size_;
30 ++i, ++i0, ++i1) {
31 if (buffer_[i0 % buffer_.size()] != b.buffer_[i1 % b.buffer_.size()]) {
32 return false;
33 }
34 }
35 return true;
36}
37
38int SaturationProtectorBuffer::Capacity() const {
39 return buffer_.size();
40}
41
42int SaturationProtectorBuffer::Size() const {
43 return size_;
44}
45
46void SaturationProtectorBuffer::Reset() {
47 next_ = 0;
48 size_ = 0;
49}
50
51void SaturationProtectorBuffer::PushBack(float v) {
52 RTC_DCHECK_GE(next_, 0);
53 RTC_DCHECK_GE(size_, 0);
54 RTC_DCHECK_LT(next_, buffer_.size());
55 RTC_DCHECK_LE(size_, buffer_.size());
56 buffer_[next_++] = v;
57 if (rtc::SafeEq(next_, buffer_.size())) {
58 next_ = 0;
59 }
60 if (rtc::SafeLt(size_, buffer_.size())) {
61 size_++;
62 }
63}
64
65absl::optional<float> SaturationProtectorBuffer::Front() const {
66 if (size_ == 0) {
67 return absl::nullopt;
68 }
69 RTC_DCHECK_LT(FrontIndex(), buffer_.size());
70 return buffer_[FrontIndex()];
71}
72
73int SaturationProtectorBuffer::FrontIndex() const {
74 return rtc::SafeEq(size_, buffer_.size()) ? next_ : 0;
75}
76
77} // namespace webrtc
